thread.title_full: Elevate Styles reviewed by Janessa Riche

author: Janessa Riche
title: Janessa Riche
text: I love the service from Electric styles. Everything was packaged well, delivery was super fast. I made my order on Saturday and got it by Monday afternoon. I love everything I picked out expecially my African wig. I am actually going to review the wigs on my YouTube channel. I will definitely be recommending everyone to this site.
